ROW.Details:
Capture mode. Sequence = 0;  DoubleExposure = 1;
Continuous = 2; AverageWithGainSequence = 3;
Average = 4;Single = 5;Integrated=6.

1622 gain correction setting. 
case 1 : None(0) --- no gain correction; 
case 2 : Offset(1) --- offset correction; 
case 3 : Gain(2) --- offset + gain + pixel
case 4 : GainSequence(3) --- offset +  gainsequence + pixel
